# This directory stores:
#   training_data.csv    — scraped historical first-goalscorer data (ML training)
#   ml_model.pkl         — trained GradientBoostingClassifier
#   ml_scaler.pkl        — StandardScaler for feature normalization
#   model_metrics.json   — training/CV metrics from last retrain
#   accuracy_log.jsonl   — daily prediction accuracy records
#
# Files are created automatically by:
#   python -m nhl_predictor.cli scrape   → training_data.csv
#   python -m nhl_predictor.cli train    → ml_model.pkl, ml_scaler.pkl, model_metrics.json
#   python -m nhl_predictor.cli track    → accuracy_log.jsonl
